com.epimorphics.lda.renderers.common

Class DisplayRdfNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epimorphics.rdfutil.RDFNodeWrapper
      • com.epimorphics.lda.renderers.common.CommonNodeWrapper
        • com.epimorphics.lda.renderers.common.DisplayRdfNode

  • public class DisplayRdfNode
extends CommonNodeWrapper
    Facade for a resource from the resultset with methods to make displaying the resource in a template easier. In particular, this class collaborates with DisplayHierarchy to unfold the results graph into a tree that can be displayed to the user.
    Author:
    Ian Dickinson, Epimorphics (mailto:ian@epimorphics.com)
